es + special districts). impact_pct = impact_usd / total_all_units_levy x 100, so it varies by county: school-tax-heavy counties score higher, counties with large city/special- district bases score lower. This is honest arithmetic on real data, not an official fiscal estimate.","source_url":"https://comptroller.texas.gov/taxes/property-tax/docs/2025-school-district-rates-levies.xlsx","fetched_at":"2026-07-04T01:57:42.951276+00:00"}